Package: flatcolor
Version: 2.4.1-2
Type: theme
Name: Theme Flatcolor
Description: Optional Theme. Dynamic Horizontal Menu.
 Works excelent in all browsers.
 Fine in IOS. (one touch -> hover), (two touch -> click).
 Ok in Android Tablets, smartphones.. (The click event has been converted to a Dashboard menu).
 The blue number circles can be removed by setting the $circle to '' in renderer.php.
